## Automated Versioning Script

Create a helper script for consistent versioning:

```powershell
# scripts/bump-version.ps1
param(
    [Parameter(Mandatory=$true)]
    [ValidateSet("patch", "minor", "major")]
    [string]$Type,
    
    [string]$Message = ""
)

cd src

# Bump version
npm version $Type -m "chore: bump version to %s`n`n$Message"

# Push commits and tags
git push
git push --tags

Write-Host "✅ Version bumped and pushed!"
```

